			<text use-page-width="false" push-down="false" lock-width="true">
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">The conjugated system of equations - this ODE system describes the change in time of the conguagted variables (functional type lagrange multiplyers) </p>
